name: Krushdemo
tagline: Created a demo for sign in/sign up with email as well as other social service.
body:
### Welcome to Krush Demo project Page.
This application is made to study new sign-in/sign-up for our other application using either mail or social logins.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
